<plot>A husband laughs at women's magazines that offer tips to help 'old maids' preserve their looks, but when he nods off, he realizes in his dream that his own wife has been availing herself of these artificial beauty aids and is in fact far older than she appears. He demands that she remove them all, to dreadful effect.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?539571</url></doc>
